Howto deploy a simple Rails application to a server

* Setup/Goal
  - Server is located in a virtual machine (using VirtualBox)
  - Linux environment (basics should also work for other OSes, adapt
    accordingly)
  - Version control: Git or Mercurial (Hg)

* Please read the file [[file:installing_rails_on_server.org]] for further details




